            </div>
            <div>
                <img class="h-auto max-w-full rounded-lg" src="https://www.themoviedb.org/t/p/w1280/oLxWocqheC8XbXbxqJ3x422j9PW.jpg" alt="Snow White movie poster">
            </div>
            <div>
