            </div>
            <div>
                <img class="h-auto max-w-full rounded-lg" src="https://www.themoviedb.org/t/p/w1280/zboCGZ4aIqPMd7VFI4HWnmc7KYJ.jpg" alt="Another Simple Favor movie poster">
